default4.5
default 
defaultLEPs 
defaultdo 
defaultincorporate a voluntary sector input,
default 
defaultbut disability is much more than just a third sector issue and it would be wrong to assume that the third sector is necessarily the best way for people with disabilities to engage. 
defaultIn summary, 
defaultwith LEPs ta
defaultking a greater role in decision 
defaultmaking, 
defaultwe want to
default see LEPs placed under a clear statutory duty to take equa
